version_description: in most versions a G chord is used in the chorus, i sincerely believe this should be an Em chord. also in other tabs it just says to play the chorus, i personally always like it if i can see the chorus again because i scroll through the song while playing. i also added how to play the chords.
This has a different (and more accurate) chord progression in the chorus as well as being a capo 7 version.
The chords could sound clearer to the song on capo 2.

song_name: Boldly I Approach The Art Of Celebration

version_description: These chords are loosely based off of Rend Collective's track found here (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WGqyi-WpHU4). This is a simplified version for ease of player, and is not in the recorded key.
This is the official chord chart from the Rend Collective website (also, it is in 4/4 time and the tempo is 77 bpm).
